### App base home
GET http://localhost:3000/


### NEW conversation
POST http://localhost:3000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Hello there. I have some questions for you. What services do you guys offer?",
  "conversation": null
}


### Existing conversation
POST http://localhost:3000/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Okay. I have a complaint about a service of yours",
  "conversation_id": "0198bf52-3b73-70ab-a355-24b4ecb345e4"
}


### Fetch chat conversations
GET http://localhost:3000/chat/0198bf52-3b73-70ab-a355-24b4ecb345e4


### Fetch all chats
GET http://localhost:3000/chat


### Admin Login (you need to be authenticated first)
POST http://localhost:3000/admin/login
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=admin&password=admin123


### Get all conversations (admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/api/conversations


### Get all conversations (admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/api/conversations


### Get specific conversation details (admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/api/conversations/0198bf52-3b73-70ab-a355-24b4ecb345e4


### Get conversation statistics (admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/api/stats


### Update conversation (admin)
PUT http://localhost:3000/admin/api/conversations/0198bf52-3b73-70ab-a355-24b4ecb345e4
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerName": "John Doe Updated",
  "channel": "email"
}


### Kill conversation (admin)
POST http://localhost:3000/admin/api/conversations/0198bf52-3b73-70ab-a355-24b4ecb345e4/kill


### Reactivate conversation (admin)
POST http://localhost:3000/admin/api/conversations/0198bf52-3b73-70ab-a355-24b4ecb345e4/reactivate


### Get all products (admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/api/products


### Get specific product (admin)
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/api/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE


### Create new product (admin)
POST http://localhost:3000/admin/api/products
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Premium Support Package",
  "price": 99.99,
  "description": "24/7 premium customer support with dedicated account manager"
}


### Update product (admin)
PUT http://localhost:3000/admin/api/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Updated Premium Support Package",
  "price": 129.99,
  "description": "24/7 premium customer support with dedicated account manager and priority response"
}


### Delete product (admin)
DELETE http://localhost:3000/admin/api/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE
